#challenge two — The Suspicious Chocolate.exe 

A shiny USB labelled 'SOCMAS Party Playlist' appears on desk. Inside there's a file called chocolate.exe.

# Objective: To determine whether chocolate.exe is safe or infected.

# Steps:
